text: Swabian German () is an Alemannic German dialect. It is mainly spoken in Swabia in central and southeastern Baden-Württemberg. It's also spoken in the capital Stuttgart and the Swabian Jura region and southwest Bavaria (Bavarian Swabia). ==References== Category:German dialects Category:Languages of Germany Category:Baden-Württemberg Category:Swabia (Bavaria)
title: Swabian German
